GET A SNEAK PEEK AT SEEING

Is vision just one way to see? How do our brains interpret what’s in front of our eyes? SEEING explores the subjectivity of sight, the other senses that shape our view of the world, and the unexpected parallels between human and machine vision. Find out more here.
